data.description: This lovely 1528 sq ft. Villa is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath, den, 2-car garage is located within walking distance to all of the Robson amenities!   This Villa is perfect for snowbirds or those that are just discovering Robson Ranch!  Brand new carpets in the two bedrooms.  Lots of natural light in the great room, dining room and den.  The den is open to the great room too!  The landscaping and exterior maintenance is taken care of for you.  This is one of the larger Villas here in Robson Ranch.  Enjoy the shaded covered back patio in the afternoon.  Come see this beautiful Villa!
